                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#83ra">Fol. 83ra</locus>-rb: Ownership note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 83ra-b: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ አእማደ፡ ምስጢር፡ ዘሐለቃ፡ ተስፋይ፡ ኰኰሎ፡ ዘውእቱ፡ ገብረ፡ ስላሴ፡ {ወብእሲቱ፡ ኂሩተ፡ ስላሴ፡} ወአቡሁ፡ መዝገበ፡ ስላሴ፡ ወደቂቁ፡ ኪነ፡ ስላሴ፡ ሐብተ፡ ስላሴ፡ ኃይለ፡ ስላሴ፡ አመተ፡ ስላሴ፡ ወለተ፡ ስላሴ፡ ጥበበ፡ ስላሴ፡ ልሕኵተ፡ ስላሴ፡ ስምረተ፡ ስላሴ፡ ወእሙ፡ ወለተ፡ እግዚእ፡ ወእማ፡ ወለተ፡ ማርያም፡ ወእህታ፡ ዓመተ፡ ጽዮን፡ ወወለታ፡ ወለተ፡ ብርሃን፡ ወእሁኁ፡ ገብረ፡ ጊዎርጊስ፡ ዘውእቱ፡ ኃለቃ፡ አባይ፡ ዘሰረቆ፡ ወዘፈሀቆ፡ ወዘተአገሎ፡ በኃይል፡ ዘዕ{ን}በለ፡ ፈቃደ፡ እግዚኡ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በስልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮ{ስ}፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ከመ፡ አርዮስ፡ ወመቅደልዮስ።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 83ra-b: This book of ʾAʿmadä mǝsṭir is of ḥaläqa Täsfayä [of] K<hi rend="apices">w</hi>äk<hi rend="apices">w</hi>älo, who is Gäbrä Sǝllase. {His wife is Ḫirutä Sǝllase} and his father Mäzgäbä Sǝllase, and his children Kinä Sǝllase, Ḥabtä Sǝllase, Ḫaylä Sǝllase, ʾAmätä Sǝllase, Wälättä Sǝllase, Ṭǝbäbä Sǝllase, Lǝḥk<hi rend="apices">w</hi>ǝtä Sǝllase, Sǝmrätä Sǝllase, and his mother Wälättä ʾƎgziʾ, and her mother Wälättä Maryam, and her sister ʿAmätä Ṣǝyon, and her daughter Wälättä Bǝrhan, and his brother Gäbrä Giyorgis that is ḫaläqa ʾAbbay. May the one who stole it or erased it or took it by force without the permission of the owner be excommunicated by the authority of Peter and Paul like Arius and Macedonius. </q>
                           The note contains a tämäläs-sign, in the shape of two perpendicular lines, indicating where the omission, written above, belongs: fol. 83ra l.8.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Omitted letters, words and passages are written interlineally, in the main hand: fols. 6vb, 46rb, 57ra, 68vb, 80vb.&#xD;
- Erasure of words: fols. 9va, 17va, 19rb, 24ra, 25vb, 43va, 44rb, 45vb, 46va, 47ra, 49va, 59ra, 60ra, 61ra, 66ra, 67vb.&#xD;
- Interlinear corrections: fols. 19v, 57ra, 68vb, 70va, 71vb.&#xD;
- A crude note: fol. 1v.</item>
